{"tid":1601020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"所有有gear 手足唔該背左佢！","createTime":"2019-09-29T00:33:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T00:38:31.000Z","uid":42870,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fce8a80119fc2d2a0e095d100e62fd6f1057b173","tid":1601020,"uid":42870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T00:33:23.000Z","msg":"《簡易程序治罪條例》第17條列明，任何人管有任何腕銬或其他為束縛人身而製造的工具或物件，或管有任何手銬、攻擊性武器、撬鎖工具、百合匙等或其他適合作非法用途的工具，意圖將其作任何非法用途，即可被罰款5,000元或監禁2年。<br />\n<br />\n執業大律師黃宇逸指出，法例條文中的「其他適合作非法用途的工具」一詞，只能理解為與「手銬、撬鎖工具、百合匙」等相類似的工具，例如螺絲批這類可以用來「爆鎖」的工具就符合相關定義。頭盔及眼罩完全不是用來「爆鎖」等用途的工具，不可能符合上述「其他適合作非法用途的工具」的定義。"},{"pid":"5a354f364ed3c076820cf507186c8c4574fc313e","tid":1601020,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T00:35:03.000Z","msg":"佢照拉你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf98542def6c4e39604f590992e6d9b442782aaf","tid":1601020,"uid":42870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5a354f364ed3c076820cf507186c8c4574fc313e","tid":1601020,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T00:35:03.000Z","msg":"佢照拉你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T00:35:33.000Z","msg":"背左先la"},{"pid":"fbdfe9afe229d898e52285bea64b6168f263db8a","tid":1601020,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T00:36:58.000Z","msg":"我無野講&gt;this"},{"pid":"3ddab7c329252916066bce7e38a98cc41193e849","tid":1601020,"uid":42870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fbdfe9afe229d898e52285bea64b6168f263db8a","tid":1601020,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T00:36:58.000Z","msg":"我無野講&gt;this"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T00:38:31.000Z","msg":"我無野講係for 拉左之後用，呢個係for 搜身既時候用"}]}